'''2014年环意自行车赛'''是第97届[[环意自行车赛|环意自行车赛]]，于2014年5月9日至6月1日进行，此次比赛是2014年UCI世界巡回赛的其中一站比赛。比赛共分为21个赛段，起点位于[[北爱尔兰|北爱尔兰]][[贝尔法斯特|贝尔法斯特]]，终点位于[[意大利|意大利]][[的里雅斯特|的里雅斯特]]，除前三个赛段在[[爱尔兰岛|爱尔兰岛]]进行外，其余赛段均在意大利境内进行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cyclingweekly.co.uk/news/latest/537019/giro-d-italia-2014-belfast-start-confirmed.html |title=Giro d'Italia 2014: Belfast start confirmed |publisher=Cycling Weekly |date=2013-02-21 |accessdate=2013-05-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130225070017/http://www.cyclingweekly.co.uk/news/latest/537019/giro-d-italia-2014-belfast-start-confirmed.html |archivedate=2013-02-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gazzetta.it/Giroditalia/2014/download/Regolamento_ita.pdf|title=Il Regolamento|date=2014|accessdate=2014-05-11|publisher=RCS Sport|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907194724/http://www.gazzetta.it/Giroditalia/2014/download/Regolamento_ita.pdf|archivedate=2020-09-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

共有22支车队参加此次比赛，其中19支为世界职业车队，另外3支为洲际职业车队<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/bardiani-csf-colombia-and-yellowfluo-handed-giro-ditalia-wildcard-invitations|title=Bardiani-CSF, Colombia and YellowFluo handed Giro d'Italia wildcard invitations|first=Barry|last=Ryan|work=Cyclingnews.com|date=2014-01-16|accessdate=2014-04-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140117215626/http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/bardiani-csf-colombia-and-yellowfluo-handed-giro-ditalia-wildcard-invitations|archivedate=2014-01-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最终来自移动之星车队的[[奈洛·金塔纳|奈洛·金塔纳]]夺得该届比赛冠军，成为历史上首位获得环意自行车赛冠军的哥伦比亚选手，他也获得了象征最佳青年车手的白衫<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/quintana-proud-to-be-first-colombian-winner-of-the-giro-ditalia |title=Quintana proud to be first Colombian winner of the Giro d'Italia |date=2014-05-31 |work=Cycling News |accessdate=2014-06-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140604084906/http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/quintana-proud-to-be-first-colombian-winner-of-the-giro-ditalia |archivedate=2014-06-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他的同胞，来自Omega Pharma-快步车队的[[Rigoberto_Urán|Rigoberto Urán]]获得第二名，来自阿斯塔纳车队的[[Fabio_Aru|Fabio Aru]]则获得第三名。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://colombiareports.com/colombia-cyclist-nairo-quintana-wins-giro-ditalia-fellow-colombian-rigoberto-uran-2nd/|title=Colombia's Nairo Quintana wins 2014 Giro d'Italia, Rigoberto Uran 2nd|publisher=Colombia Reports|date=2014-06-01|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200929174923/https://colombiareports.com/colombia-cyclist-nairo-quintana-wins-giro-ditalia-fellow-colombian-rigoberto-uran-2nd/|archivedate=2020-09-29}}</ref>

